WE will never use this company ever again and we note to all of our vendors that we will not accept deliveries from XPO Logistics. 
If you want to have a good day and a great delivery experience steer clear of these folks.







They delivered my new washer and dryer, but instead of giving us the information and the opportunity to take off the power cord, they took it with them despite the fact that it has been discussed up front that I was going to keep it. 

When I called them to try and rectify the situation all they did was give me the runaround and a response of,  "too bad, so sorry".

Their customer service was awful!

Thankfully, the Sears Outlet that I purchased the units from, stepped up and did the right thing.







            XPO Logistics
        






